Refer to this bug: https://bugs.php.net/bug.php?id=72362, you can use an undocumented option **OPENSSL_DONT_ZERO_PAD_KEY** to solve this problem.

    openssl_encrypt(&quot;Text&quot;,&quot;BF-CBC&quot;,&quot;SECRETKEY&quot;,OPENSSL_DONT_ZERO_PAD_KEY,&quot;abcdefgh&quot;);

Otherwise you need manually pad the key up to a rational size.

    openssl_encrypt(&quot;Text&quot;,&quot;BF-CBC&quot;,&quot;SECRETKEYSECRETKEY&quot;,0,&quot;abcdefgh&quot;);

